snippet.title: Exoprimal – Season 4 Overview
snippet.description:
Exoprimal Season 4 drops April 17! Gear up for the wargames with six new Beta variant exosuits, Custom Matches that also allow you to progress the story as you play, Time Loop Rebellion - a variation of the game's final mission with special rewards - and a fiendish 10-player co-op crossover event with the Yellow Devil from the Mega Man series that can earn you Mega Man-themed rewards!

#Exoprimal #MegaMan #Capcom
